      !  Added check for ppm_initialized.
      !
      !  Revision 1.6  2004/05/27 14:49:58  ivos
      !  Bugfix: info was not caught after CALL to ppm_doio.
      !
      !  Revision 1.5  2004/05/27 10:41:56  ivos
